      "content": "That's a good start for the high-level concepts. For a competitive debate, though, they need more granular arguments to handle the actual rounds. Could you break down a few more specific points? Maybe something regarding the economic impact of unregulated immigration or the strain on public infrastructure/social services? I want them to have these hard-hitting points ready to go.",
